{
  "stem": "22840.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Which for me was a big mountain, but now being in Slovakia, it was a little hill.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there's another little village just [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] half a kilometer, or even less, 300 meters away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "These are little villages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was taken there for interrogation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a road going up there, and there was a house on the top of the mountain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And everybody was waiting for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And suddenly, the man is coming down the mountain, alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, coming down the mountain-- obviously alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "These were the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was interrogated by the Wehrmacht, by the Commander of the patrol of the people who-- and he told him, yes, there were partisans sleeping there at night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We cannot do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We like you Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We-- we are terrorized by the partisans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They are stealing from us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They are undisciplined.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "If you stay here, they can't do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A couple of weeks later, the Vlasovsty came and searched, and didn't find anything, because the Germans cleaned everything up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But they find something somewhere else, didn't like somebody, and killed everybody there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They didn't interrogate, just killed them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were executed next to the house where I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There is a plaque that I-- it was 10, 15 meters from the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They just shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I don't know what they found, maybe a scarf.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They would find these cartridges, we all will be shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That was the difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't want to justify the Germans, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but my fear in that village was from the SS and from the Vlasovsty.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
